headline: Norfolk Southern to announce fourth quarter 2024 earnings results Jan. 29
summary: Norfolk Southern Corporation (NYSE: NSC) will announce its fourth quarter 2024 financial results during a live conference call and internet webcast at 8:45 a.m. ET on Wednesday, Jan. 29, 2025. Quarterly earnings results will be released in advance of the call and a press release will be posted on the Investors page of the company's website.
